summary: Experienced Arabic Teacher for non-native speakers and course Coordinator with a demonstrated history of working in the higher education industry. Skilled in Communication, English, Arabic, Teamwork, and Training. Strong professional with a MA in teaching Arabic as a foreign language from the American University in Cairo.
